metadata.description:
This channel serves the site http://mac.are.na , a collaborative music player.

To contribute, add youtube, soundcloud or mp3s to a channel (any other types will be ignored), and then connect that channel here!

Source code here: https://github.com/broskoski/mac.are.na

metadata.description:
are.na mixer

This channel serves as the entry point to https://mixer-lovat.vercel.app/ (alpha)

Create channels with SoundCloud and Youtube links or other channels and connect them here.

The source is open
https://github.com/eufekt/mixer

(mac.are.na with visuals)

Currently closed channel going through testing with friends.
